How can my aura be detected in a picture?

Through spiritual connection and intuitive abilities, our aura readers interpret the subtle energetic vibrations present in a photograph. The photo serves as a bridge connecting the specialist to the energy of the person depicted. 

 

Our aura readers feel the energy flowing from the aura field. Some perceive energy as colors, while others may visualize images or experience physical sensations in their bodies related to the person's aura. 

 

For instance, if a person's energy is very intense and full of passion, the specialist might feel warmth in their body, indicating a red aura. Conversely, calm and balanced energy may evoke feelings of lightness or coolness, suggesting a blue aura. Through this connection and skill set, our specialists can accurately determine the aura color, reflecting the emotional and spiritual state of the person in the photo.

Can I choose a different necklace color if I don’t like the one from my aura analysis?

We will clearly label the analysis, so you’ll know which aura and necklace belong to you.

How long does it take to receive my necklace, and can I track my order?

You’ll receive your aura analysis within 24 hours. Your custom necklace will be shipped right after the analysis is complete, and it will take 7-9 days to arrive. Once shipped, you’ll receive a tracking number to follow its delivery.

Is the necklace made of stainless steel, and how do I care for it?

Yes, our necklaces are made from high-quality stainless steel that won’t tarnish or fade. To keep it looking great, just clean it occasionally with a soft cloth.
